mkdocs.yml.description: MkDocs configuration file with Material theme and mkdocstrings plugin. Uses Google-style docstrings. Source code path is set to 'src' directory. Navigation structure includes Home, API Reference (core, featurestore, tasks), and Examples sections.

.venv/.description: Virtual environment for documentation tooling with MkDocs 1.6.1, mkdocs-material 9.7.1, mkdocstrings 1.0.0. Use 'source .venv/bin/activate && python -m mkdocs build' to build docs.

docs/audit/docstring_coverage.md.description: Docstring coverage audit document analyzing 16 core modules. Key findings: 4 modules complete (validation.py, db_utils.py, context.py, configuration.py), 4 partial (core_utils.py, entity.py, account.py, exceptions/*), 8 missing (__init__.py, project.py, flow.py, workspace.py, common_artifact.py, request.py, models.py, utils/__init__.py). Priority enhancement order established for Phases 3-5.
